<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,1397,1782]" pageId="5" pageNumber="506">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,407,1433,1458]" pageId="5" pageNumber="506">Female genitalia.</emphasis>
Seventh sternite longer medially than sixth, lateral angles of posterior margin rounded, posterior margin medially produced with median concavity, lateral margins of concavity pointed, area adjacent to median projection concave, median projection shorter than lateral rounded angles. Eighth tergite in ventral view extending to 0.75 length of pygofer lobe and as wide as pygofer lobe,
</paragraph>
